'''Milligan College''' is a [[Christian]] [[liberal arts]] [[college]] founded in 1866 and located immediately outside of [[Elizabethton, Tennessee|Elizabethton]] in [[Carter County, Tennessee]]. The school has a student population of just over 1,000 students as well as a {{convert|181|acre|km2|sing=on}} campus that is located just minutes from downtown [[Johnson City, Tennessee]]. Like many colleges and universities, it has its own [[zip code]], 37682.
